      "span_text": "The subjects were invited to participate in the study using a Facebook-based snowball method [CITATION_1] , namely by posting an invitation to participate in \"an experiment searching for associations between keeping dogs and cats and health status and personality of subject\" on the wall of the Facebook page \"Guinea Pigs\" for Czech and Slovak nationals willing to take part in diverse evolutionary psychological experiments (www.facebook.com/pokusnikralici).",
